@startuml ToBePrescriptionFlow
title To-Be Rx Flow with Rhapsody & FHIR

skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
}

left to right direction

rectangle "Source Clinical /\nPrescribing Systems\n(multiple EHRs,\ntelehealth, etc.)" as Source

rectangle "Rhapsody Integration Platform\n\n- API Gateway / FHIR Endpoint\n- Structural Validation (FHIR)\n- Business & Compliance Rules\n- Routing & Transformation\n- Logging & Observability\n- Event Export (Analytics/Audit)" as Rhapsody

rectangle "Downstream Fulfillment\nPlatforms\n(hospital pharmacy,\nretail, mail-order,\nHUB, etc.)" as Targets

rectangle "Enterprise Analytics / Data\nPlatform\n(DWH / Data Lake)" as AnalyticsStore
rectangle "Enterprise Compliance / Audit\nTrail Store" as AuditStore

Source --> Rhapsody : FHIR REST\ntransaction (Bundle)
Rhapsody --> Targets : Routed\ntransaction\n(FHIR/HL7/other)
Rhapsody --> AnalyticsStore : Event / data\nexport
Rhapsody --> AuditStore : Audit-log /\ntraceability events

@enduml
